OL,3,CWoman in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing incident - man arrested
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted murder after a woman was
OL,8,Ffound with stab wounds in a house.
OL,10,FThe victim, in her 30s, was left in a
OL,11,Fcritical condition after the attack in
OL,12,FWarwick Street, Church, where
OL,13,FLancashire police officers found her
OL,14,Fafter 10:40 on Sunday morning (15
OL,15,FMarch 2026).
OL,17,FThe woman was taken to hospital for
OL,18,Ftreatment, it's believed she had been
OL,19,Fstabbed 'multiple times'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
