OL,3,CWoman in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing incident - man arrested
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man from Church ,in the
OL,7,FHyndburn area of Lancashire, was
OL,8,Farrested and the investigation was
OL,9,Fcontinuing.
OL,11,FA Lancashire Constabulary spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is being treated as an
OL,13,Fisolated incident between people known
OL,14,Fto each other.
OL,16,FHowever, reassurance patrols will be
OL,17,Fincreased in the area as a precaution,
OL,18,Fand there will also be a number of
OL,19,Fofficers in the area carrying out
OL,20,Fenquiries.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
