OL,3,CWoman in critical condition after
OL,4,Cstabbing incident - man arrested
OL,6,F"If you have any concerns or you have
OL,7,Fany information which could assist our
OL,8,Finvestigation, then please stop an
OL,9,Fofficer for a chat.
OL,11,FOne witness said: "Something very
OL,12,Fserious happened near the top of
OL,13,FWarwick Street, Church. Ten police
OL,14,Fvehicles, three ambulances, air
OL,15,Fambulance."
OL,17,F"Now police blue tape across the grass
OL,18,Fand a police officer standing outside.
OL,19,FOne ambulance went down Warwick
OL,20,FStreet, blue lights on and a police
OL,21,Fescort."
